import routes from '../../Images/Routes.svg'
import create from '../../Images/criar.svg'
import events from '../../Images/eventos.svg'
import savedR from '../../Images/rotasG.svg'
import insti from '../../Images/Institutions.svg'
import myevent from '../../Images/myEvents.svg'
import prize from '../../Images/Prizes.svg'
import companions from '../../Images/companions.svg'

export const homeObjZero = {

    id: 'events',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: '',
    headline: 'Events',
    description: 'The world of volunteering is waiting for you!',
    buttonLabel: 'XXXX',
    imgStart: true,
    img: routes,
    alt: 'events',
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
}
export const homeObjOne = {

    id: 'create',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: '',
    headline: 'Create an Event',
    description: 'Join an event or create your own. The options are almost limitless. Grasp the bliss of nature with an offroad adventure or share the beautiful places in your hometown, all while making a positive impact on a strangers life!',
    buttonLabel: 'XXXX',
    imgStart: true,
    img: create,
    alt: "create",
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
}

export const homeObjTwo = {

    id: 'join',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: '',
    headline: 'Join an Event',
    description: 'Join an event and experience the path with your peers',
    buttonLabel: 'XXXX',
    imgStart: true,
    img: events,
    alt: 'join',
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
}
export const homeObjThree = {

    id: 'Sroutes',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: '',
    headline: 'Try out previous Events',
    description: 'Experience a prior Event on your own. We have them all saved here!',
    buttonLabel: 'XXXX',
    imgStart: true,
    img: savedR,
    alt: 'Sroutes',
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
}

export const homeObjFour = {

    id: 'inst',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: '',
    headline: 'Institutions',
    description: 'Get to know the instituitions available for volunteering in Portugal.',
    buttonLabel: 'XXXX',
    imgStart: false,
    img: insti,
    alt: "inst",
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true,
}

export const homeObjFive = {

    id: 'myE',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: '',
    headline: 'My Events',
    description: 'All your events are saved here',
    buttonLabel: 'XXXX',
    imgStart: false,
    img: myevent,
    alt: "myE",
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true,
}
export const homeObjSix = {
    id: 'prizes',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: '',
    headline: 'Prizes',
    description: 'Here you can win more than experience through volunteering.',
    buttonLabel: 'XXXX',
    imgStart: true,
    img: prize,
    alt: 'prizes',
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true,
}
export const homeObjSeven = {

    id: 'companions',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText:true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine:'',
    headline: 'Volunteer Companions',
    description: '',
    buttonLabel: 'XXXX',
    imgStart: false,
    img: companions,
    alt:"companions",
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true,
}

export const homeObjProfile = {

    id: 'profile',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: '',
    headline: 'Profile',
    primary: true,
}
